room_title: Escape room "Zen Room" by 60out Escape Rooms in Los Angeles
room_address: 13336 Beach Ave Marina Del Rey, CA 90292
room_description: Welcome to your dream! After being put into a deep trance, you enter a room that is all white, blank, and a bit bizarre. Your mind has conjured a series of tricks and challenges that you must overcome to bring color back to this world.
